        "image_position": "left",
        "eyebrow": "Reverse Osmosis",
        "heading": "The Most Thorough Filtration Available.",
        "body_text": "Reverse osmosis forces water through a semi-permeable membrane fine enough to reject dissolved solids, heavy metals, and other trace contaminants that lighter filtration methods can miss — typically the most complete filtration technology sold for home use. It runs under the sink, uses a small storage tank, and delivers filtered water on demand at the tap. HAUSTAS Reserve Max pairs RO with a multi-stage pre-filter for full coverage.",
